WEBVTT

1
00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:48.550 
因为回家而郁闷
unhappy to be back,

2
00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:50.860 
在所有不该松散的地方松散
slack in all the wrong spots.

3
00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:52.670 
体面的西装发出阵阵恶臭
Seamy suit of clothes,

4
00:16:52.670 --> 00:16:55.180 
又脏又破
dishrag-ratty, worn.

5
00:16:57.940 --> 00:16:59.480 
你回了家
You return home,

6
00:17:00.420 --> 00:17:01.840 
就像登上了月球
moon-landed,

7
00:17:02.960 --> 00:17:04.020 
到了外太空
foreign.

8
00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:08.340 
地心引力拉扯
The Earth's gravitational pull,

9
00:17:08.380 --> 00:17:10.430 
现在有了双倍效果
an effort now redoubled...

10
00:17:11.470 --> 00:17:14.420 
将你的鞋带拉松
Dragging your shoelaces loose...

11
00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:16.570 
还有你的肩膀
And your shoulders,

12
00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:21.420 
把忧虑的章节在你额头刻得更深
etching deeper the stanza of worry on your forehead.

